<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTA53">
<l>oṉṟuṇṭu ceṅkaṇmāl yāṉuraippa tuṉṉaṭiyārk</l>
<l>keṉceyva ṉeṉṟē yiruttinī niṉpukaḻil</l>
<l>vaikumtañ cintaiyilu maṟṟiṉitō nīyavarkku</l>
<l>vaikunta meṉṟaruḷum vāṉ.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>There is something, red-eyed Māl, I have to say. Thinking</l>
<l>“what shall I do” for your servants, you may start [something]. In all their minds</l>
<l>that are directed on your fame, is there anything else as sweet,</l>
<l>[even] the heaven that you may grant them with Vaikuntam?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
